== Home of Harmless Amination & Comic

=== 安装所需软件包
# yum install ruby
# yum install ruby-mysql
# yum install ruby-sqlite3
# yum install rubygems

# gem install rails --include-dependencies
# gem install mongrel


=== SVN签出
$ svn checkout https://hhac2.googlecode.com/svn/trunk/ hhac2 --username XXX
$ cd hhac2


=== 数据库的配置
$ mysql -uroot -p -e "CREATE DATABASE IF NOT EXISTS hhac2"
$ mysql -uroot -p -e "GRANT ALL PRIVILEGES ON hhac2.* TO hhac"

$ rake db:migrate


=== 测试－启动服务
$ ./script/server
